    "body": "**Problem:** latest GCC 17 snapshot warns in `run_scratch_tests` that a zeroed stack scratch object may be passed to `free()`.\r\n**Fix:** Use the existing heap-allocated scratch object for the invalid scratch-space checks, zero it before the checks, and free it manually afterwards.",
